<div id="home-content">
    <div id="dashboard-image"><%= image_tag "cricket8.jpg", :size => "440x250" %></div>
    <div id="whatisit-text">
        <div class="blurb_about">Doosra Cricket</div>
        <div  class="blurb_about_line" style="padding-left:25px;color:#3B5998;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;">Predict, Discuss, Win and <br/> Show your expertise</div>
        <div  class="blurb_about_line" style="padding-left:80px;color:#3B5998;;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;">on matches</div>
        <div  class="blurb_about_line" style="padding-left:40px;color:#3B5998;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;">Publically or Privately</div>
    </div>
    

     <div id="how-to-get-started">
 
        <div class="blurb_about">How does it work?</div>

        <div style="color:#5B5B5B;font-size:50px;font-family:Georgia;font-weight:bold;float:left;padding:0px 10px;">1</div>
        <div  class="blurb_about_line">Pick a Fixture and Join or Start a Contest.<br/>
        <span style="font-size:16px;font-family:Georgia;padding-left:30px;">Either join a open contest or start a private contest for your group</span><br/></div>
        <div style="clear: both; padding-top: 10px;"></div>

       <div style="color:#5B5B5B;font-size:50px;font-family:Georgia;font-weight:bold;float:left;padding:0px 10px;">2</div>
       <div  class="blurb_about_line">Invite your friends to the contest<br/>
         <span style="font-size:16px;font-family:Georgia;padding-left:30px;">Include friends that you know would be interested AND/OR</span><br/>
         <span style="font-size:16px;font-family:Georgia;padding-left:30px;margin-top:5px;">Share an Open invite via email to let them know about the contest</span><br/>
         <span style="font-size:16px;font-family:Georgia;padding-left:30px;margin-top:5px;">so that those interested can then choose to join.</span> </div>
       <div style="clear: both; padding-top: 20px;"></div>

       <div style="color:#5B5B5B;font-size:50px;font-family:Georgia;font-weight:bold;float:left;padding:0px 10px;">3</div>
       <div class="blurb_about_line">Cast your Predictions for each match on various categories<br/>
         <span style="font-size:16px;font-family:Georgia;padding-left:30px;">Show off your expertise and see who comes out ahead</span><br/>
       </div>   
       <div style="clear: both; padding-top: 20px;"></div>

       <div style="color:#5B5B5B;font-size:50px;font-family:Georgia;font-weight:bold;float:left;padding:0px 10px;">4</div>
       <div class="blurb_about_line">Once the match is over, results get tabulated and displayed<br/>
         <span style="font-size:16px;font-family:Georgia;padding-left:30px;">Watch everyone's score and See who really knows their game :)</span><br/>
       </div>
       <div style="clear: both; padding-top: 20px;"></div>

       <div style="color:#5B5B5B;font-size:50px;font-family:Georgia;font-weight:bold;float:left;padding:0px 10px;">5</div>
       <div class="blurb_about_line">All along, discuss the match by posting comments<br/>
         <span style="font-size:16px;font-family:Georgia;padding-left:30px;">News, Strategies, Gossip - anything you wish</span><br/>
       </div>
       <div style="clear: both; padding-top: 20px;"></div>

    </div>

